      <div class="not-prose my-4 border border-border p-4 bg-muted/30">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono">"I want to add [feature]. Here's a similar feature in the codebase: [paste code]. Help me create my version following the same patterns."</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="not-prose my-4 border border-border p-4 bg-muted/30">
        <p class="text-sm font-mono">"I got this error: [paste error]. Here's the code that caused it: [paste code]. What's wrong and how do I fix it?"</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="not-prose my-4 border border-border p-4 bg-muted/30">
